in North Carolina.

39:43.652 --> 39:45.385
"In exchange
for her guilty plea,

39:45.437 --> 39:48.188
"ms. Davis was convicted
of conspiracy to commit fraud,

39:48.239 --> 39:52.159
a reduced sentence that carries
with it a shorter prison term."

39:52.226 --> 39:56.246
♪ To your beating heart ♪

39:56.331 --> 39:59.232
♪ your beating heart ♪

39:59.284 --> 40:05.005
♪ your beating heart ♪

40:06.958 --> 40:12.012
♪ In the worst of all
the best times that we shared ♪

