40:32.117 --> 40:33.951
"quarterback Troy jameson.

40:34.019 --> 40:36.487
The Arkansas prospect
continues to hold out."

40:36.554 --> 40:38.522
You look pretty.

40:41.793 --> 40:45.445
♪ And in the black of night ♪

40:46.581 --> 40:52.669
♪ I would ask you to be mine ♪

40:52.754 --> 40:54.638
hi.

40:54.723 --> 40:57.274
God, I missed you.

40:57.342 --> 40:59.843
Is this heaven?

40:59.928 --> 41:01.845
No.

41:01.930 --> 41:05.232
Just my version of it.

